last_episode_to_air.name: Hitozuma Cosplay Kissa: Cosplay Cafe
last_episode_to_air.overview:
There is a coffee shop that attracts many customers, but not because of coffee, but because the servants are all MILF women who wear clothes that are not normally worn by servants in general.

But the story is more important in the love life of Asahina Tomoya the temporary owner of the coffee shop.
